<img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1719288 lazyload lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Mr-Eazi-Temi-Otedola.jpeg" alt="" width="1280" height="1605" /> Lovebirds Mr Eazi and Temi Otedola are set to tie the knot after the singer proposed to her today.   Sharing her proposal in an 18 seconds clip on her Twitter with the caption just including the infinity sign, the internet has gone viral with the news.   A post shared by Temiloluwa Otedola (@temiotedola) In the 38 seconds soundless video, we watched and awwed as Mr Eazi got down on one knee, asking the billionaire heiress to spend forever with him. The couple who have been together for four years have made shared with fans breathtakingly beautiful moments from their relationships, from spending time together to trips abroad and their well known big surprises on either of their birthdays. Back in 2021, the two started their own podcast, How Far, where they talk about their relationship and the dos and don’ts in a relationship. Many Nigerians have trooped to the lovebirds’ social media pages to wish them a happy married life.